[0.000, "o", "Use of this INI entry is deprecated, use global input_encoding instead.\r\u001b[58d;"]
[0.000, "o", " If empty, default_charset or input_encoding or iconv.input_encoding is used.\r\u001b[59d"]
[0.000, "o", "; The precedence is: default_charset < input_encoding < iconv.input_encoding\r\u001b[60d;iconv.input_encoding =\u001b[K\r\u001b[61d\u001b[K\u001b[62d"]
