[0.000, "o", "; Use of this INI entry is deprecated, use global internal_encoding instead.\u001b[40;3Hinternal/script encoding.\u001b[K\r\u001b[41d; Some encoding cannot work as internal encoding. (e.g. SJIS, BIG5, ISO-2022-*)\r\u001b[42d"]
[0.000, "o", "; If empty, default_charset or internal_encoding or iconv.internal_encoding is used.\u001b[43;3HThe precedence is: default_charset < internal_encoding < iconv.internal_encoding\r\u001b[44d;mbstring.internal_encoding =\u001b[K\u001b[46;3HUse of this INI entry is deprecated, use global input_encoding instead.\r\u001b[47d;"]
[0.000, "o", " http input encoding.\u001b[K\r\u001b[48d; mbstring.encoding_translation = On is needed to use this setting.\r\u001b[49d"]
[0.000, "o", "; If empty, default_charset or input_encoding or mbstring.input is used.\u001b[50;3HThe precedence is: default_charset < input_encoding < mbstring.http_input\r\u001b[51d; https://php.net/mbstring.http-input\r\u001b[52d;mbstring.http_input =\r\u001b[53d"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[K\u001b[54d; Use of this INI entry is deprecated, use global output_encoding instead.\r\u001b[55d; http output encoding.\r\u001b[56d"]
[0.000, "o", "; mb_output_handler must be registered as output buffer to function.\u001b[57;3HIf empty, default_charset or output_encoding or mbstring.http_output is used.\u001b[58;3HThe precedence is: default_charset < output_encoding < mbstring.http_output\u001b[K\u001b[59;4H"]
[0.000, "o", "o use an output encoding conversion, mbstring's output handler must be set\r\u001b[60d; otherwise output encoding conversion cannot be performed.\r\u001b[61d"]
